### ğŸ§  Agents (fixed roles)
- **Initiators** â€“ Propose moral rules or actions  
- **Validators** â€“ Evaluate based on memory + reputation  
- **Observers** â€“ Log actions and detect contradictions  
- **Rogues** â€“ Introduce ethical chaos or disruptive proposals  
- **Archivists** â€“ Review past decisions and validate memory consistency  

### ğŸ—ƒï¸ Ledger
All decisions and trust shifts are recorded permanently. Logs include:
- Event timestamp  
- Agent role + ID  
- Action proposed  
- Validation outcome  
- Trust change (if any)  
- Ethics Node deviation check  

### ğŸ§ª Scenario Variables
Customizable parameters for simulation:
- Resource scarcity  
- Conflicting moral priorities  
- Trust asymmetry  
- Isolation / censorship  
- Temporal compression (simulate centuries of drift)

